&lt;p&gt;Ward 14 is a busy 14 bedded in patient oncology unit providing a wide range of care to patients with cancer.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are a highly motivated Registered Nurse and can demonstrate an ability to respond to change in a positive manner we would like to meet you. You will be joining a well-established team whose philosophy is to deliver the best possible care to patients. The patient is central to our beliefs and values and is a unique individual who deserves the right to receive healthcare in a safe, timely manner in an environment that is appropriate to their needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate must be able to demonstrate excellent communication skills, be enthusiastic, innovative and above all be patient focused.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants must be able to work flexibly across a range of shift patterns.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Paula Harrison (Ward Manager)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
